captions.text: My favorite Champion is Twisted Fate, TF for short.
I think he is a very graceful and flexible Champion.
He is a pretty powerful AP carry and his appearance is very cool. I think that he’s my style of Champion.
I like to be flexible when I’m playing a game; I like to support my team and gank.
When I play this Champion into the late game, I feel like we are one.
I utilize the unique strengths of this Champion to help my top lane, bottom lane, and jungler
Doing this is very helpful to supporting my team, and keeping the lanes pushed.
I play a very important role for my team by playing this Champion.
When you reach level six, you need to provide help for your teammates,
such as jungling, top lane and bot lane support, so that you can become a threat to the enemy team.
I think the precise card-switch and the timing of his ult is the most important skill for TF.
The other Champions I like to have on my team are Rammus, Alistar and Taric;
mostly Champions with a lot of crowd control.
My name is Yu “Misaya” Jingxi, my team is World Elite, and my favorite Champion is Twisted Fate.

title: Pro Player Pick: Misaya Picks Twisted Fate
